        <description>&lt;hr /&gt;&#13;
&lt;h3&gt;Update Action History Status Max Retries&lt;/h3&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;The maximum number of times to retry getting the status of an action from the Tanium Action History table. &lt;br /&gt;&#13;
The "Tanium-Update Action Status" Flow will execute a loop every 5 minutes until this number of retries has been reached. For example, setting this to 96 loops will result in the Flow continuing to retry getting the Action status until a "final" status is detected, or until 8 hours (96 * 5 / 60) have elapsed. &lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong&gt;Default&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;i&gt;144&lt;/i&gt; (~12 hours)</description>
